45,104", "bbox": [609.4, 674.6, 708.3, 697.7]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [740.6, 674.6, 756.1, 697.7]}, {"text": "39,235", "bbox": [778.4, 674.6, 839.6, 697.7]}, {"text": "$ 284,339", "bbox": [871.9, 674.6, 970.8, 697.7]}, {"text": "10. Leases", "bbox": [75.0, 722.9, 175.3, 746.0]}, {"text": "The Company leases certain property and equipment under non-cancelable leases.  Office and equipment leases are", "bbox": [150.0, 770.5, 1139.4, 793.6]}, {"text": "generally for terms of three to five years and generally provide renewal options for terms of up to an additional three years.", "bbox": [112.5, 794.5, 1144.2, 817.6]}, {"text": "Model home leases are generally for shorter terms approximating one year with renewal options on a month-to-month basis.", "bbox": [112.5, 818.4, 1144.2, 841.5]}, {"text": "In most cases, management expects that in the normal course of business, leases that expire will be renewed or replaced by", "bbox": [112.5, 842.4, 1139.3, 865.5]}, {"text": "other leases.  The future minimum lease payments required under operating leases that have initial or remaining non-", "bbox": [112.5, 866.3, 1134.3, 889.4]}, {"text": "cancelable terms in excess of one year are as follows ($000’s omitted):", "bbox": [112.5, 890.3, 698.4, 913.4]}, {"text": "Years Ending December 31,", "bbox": [300.0, 938.4, 548.8, 961.6]}, {"text": "2005......................................................", "bbox": [375.0, 986.2, 693.0, 1009.3]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [737.7, 986.2, 753.2, 1009.3]}, {"text": "46,337", "bbox": [794.1, 986.2, 855.3, 1009.3]}, {"text": "2006......................................................", "bbox": [375.0, 1010.1, 693.0, 1033.2]}, {"text": "38,035", "bbox": [794.1, 1010.1, 855.4, 1033.2]}, {"text": "2007......................................................", "bbox": [375.0, 1034.1, 698.0, 1057.2]}, {"text": "32,929", "bbox": [794.1, 1034.1, 855.4, 1057.2]}, {"text": "2008......................................................", "bbox": [375.0, 1058