Company, in the normal course of business, had outstanding letters of credit and", "bbox": [150.0, 1465.5, 1139.3, 1488.6]}, {"text": "performance bonds of $1.8 billion and $1.4 billion, respectively.", "bbox": [112.5, 1489.4, 641.1, 1512.5]}, {"text": "51", "bbox": [594.2, 1552.1, 614.9, 1575.2]}]}